title: S&P will rise to 2900 by year's end, says a "nervously neutral" Lisa Erickson
text:
S&P will rise to 2900 by year's end, says a "nervously neutral" Lisa Erickson 12:44am IST - 04:29
U.S. Bank's head of traditional investments is bullish about the consumer. She tells Reuters' Fred Katayama she favors consumer discretionary and IT stocks.
